# Features

OrionHealth is a privacy-first medical AI application with offline capabilities.

## Core Features

### 🔒 Privacy-First Architecture
- **100% Offline**: All medical data stored locally on device using Isar database
- **End-to-End Encryption**: AES-256-GCM encryption for data at rest and in transit
- **Self-Sovereign Identity**: SSI implementation for secure data sharing
- **No Cloud Dependency**: Your data never leaves your device

### 🏥 Medical Data Management
- **Comprehensive Health Records**: Store and manage medical history, prescriptions, allergies
- **ICD-10, LOINC, SNOMED CT Integration**: International medical standards compliance
- **Document Upload with OCR**: Scan and digitize medical documents
- **BLE Medical Device Integration**: Connect to heart rate monitors, glucose sensors

### 🤖 AI Medical Assistant
- **On-Device LLM**: Gemma 4B GGUF running locally via llama.cpp
- **Privacy-Preserving**: Medical queries processed locally, no data sent to cloud
- **RAG Enrichment**: Medical knowledge base for accurate responses
- **Multi-language Support**: English and Spanish medical terminology

### 📡 Secure Data Sharing
- **BLE (Bluetooth Low Energy)**: Share health data with nearby devices
- **NFC**: Near-field communication for quick data transfer
- **WiFi Direct**: High-bandwidth sharing for large medical files
- **Consent-Based**: All sharing requires explicit user consent

### 📊 Analytics & Insights
- **Vital Signs Tracking**: Monitor heart rate, oxygen, temperature
- **Trend Analysis**: Historical data visualization
- **Privacy-Conscious**: All analytics run locally

## Technical Stack

| Component | Technology |
|-----------|------------|
| Framework | Flutter 3.x |
| Database | Isar (local, encrypted) |
| AI | Gemma 4B GGUF + Ollama |
| Encryption | AES-256-GCM, Argon2id |
| BLE | flutter_blue_plus 2.3.1 |
| Standards | ICD-10, LOINC, SNOMED CT |

## Security Features

- **Encryption at Rest**: All data encrypted with AES-256-GCM
- **Encryption in Transit**: TLS-like security for BLE/WiFi sharing
- **Biometric Authentication**: Fingerprint/face unlock for app access
- **PIN Protection**: Backup authentication method
- **Secure Key Derivation**: Argon2id for password hashing

## Platform Support

- **Android**: Primary platform with full feature support
- **iOS**: Coming soon
- **Linux**: Development and testing supported

## Future Roadmap

- [ ] Health insurance integration
- [ ] Telemedicine appointments
- [ ] Multi-device sync via SSI
- [ ] Apple Health / Google Fit integration
